## Feature Gating for Monetization 💰

**Privacy and beautiful UX are FREE forever. Premium features can be gated.**

### Free Tier (Always Free)

✅ **Core productivity features:**
- Unlimited notes (once Notes MVP ships)
- Unlimited tasks (Kanban)
- Unlimited calendar events
- Unlimited time tracking
- Unlimited habits
- Local storage (unlimited via IndexedDB)
- Manual export/import (.brain files)
- File System Access API auto-save
- All privacy features (encryption, local-first)
- Beautiful UX (no ads, no nags)

✅ **Privacy features (always free):**
- End-to-end encryption
- Local-first storage
- Zero telemetry
- User-controlled backups

**Philosophy:** Core "Second Brain" functionality should be free forever. We compete on privacy and UX, not paywalls.

